OL,3,CRadio 4 LW/MW, linear BBC services and
OL,4,Cfuture BBC funding
OL,6,GIt is always risky to look into the
OL,7,Gfuture and presume an outcome.
OL,9,FThe direction of travel at a
OL,10,Fparticular point in time may be clear.
OL,11,FBut the final destination and the time
OL,12,Fof arrival may be different matters.
OL,14,FIt was widely presumed by many that
OL,15,FRadio 4's long wave transmissions
OL,16,Fwould be stopping in the next few
OL,17,Fweeks.
OL,19,FSeparate programmes on Radio 4 LW are
OL,20,Fabout to stop ` the Daily Service and
OL,21,FYesterday in Parliament will transfer
OL,22,Fto Radio 4 Extra.
