OL,3,CRadio 4 LW/MW, linear BBC services and
OL,4,Cfuture BBC funding
OL,6,FThey will need to be convinced that it
OL,7,Fis a service worth buying ` perhaps
OL,8,FUHD or a seamless bridge between
OL,9,Flinear and on-demand services.
OL,11,FEven if Freeview does become a legacy
OL,12,FI cannot imagine it going until only a
OL,13,Ftiny number of people are using it.
OL,14,FAnd to simply assume it will become a
OL,15,Flegacy is quite a jump.
OL,17,FA few years ago some in the radio
OL,18,Findustry were keen to set a date for
OL,19,Fswitching off all FM transmissions to
OL,20,Fencourage digital radio. How does that
OL,21,Flook now? Even prehistoric LW is being
OL,22,Fkept open now for a tiny audience.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/12
