OL,3,CRadio 4 LW/MW, linear BBC services and
OL,4,Cfuture BBC funding
OL,6,FPlenty of people still seem happy
OL,7,Fenough to watch SD Freeview channels.
OL,9,FIn the event that Sky eventually
OL,10,Fceases satellite transmissions and
OL,11,FFreesat consequently becomes unviable,
OL,12,FI can just imagine the BBC and others
OL,13,Fpointing out that their channels are
OL,14,Fstill on Freeview.
OL,16,FFreesat was initially launched to help
OL,17,Fpeople in the areas where only
OL,18,Fanalogue TV was broadcast prior to
OL,19,Fswitchover.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/12
