OL,3,CRadio 4 LW/MW, linear BBC services and
OL,4,Cfuture BBC funding
OL,6,FIt is also worth cautioning against
OL,7,Fpresuming that the end of the TV
OL,8,FLicence is near even if some evolution
OL,9,Fmay be possible.
OL,11,FThe unveiling of the government's
OL,12,Fexpert panel on alternatives received
OL,13,Fhardly any attention.
OL,15,FOne reason for that, of course, is
OL,16,Fthat there is the small matter of the
OL,17,FGeneral Election.
