OL,3,CRadio 4 LW/MW, linear BBC services and
OL,4,Cfuture BBC funding
OL,6,FAt the point of writing, it would seem
OL,7,Fthat there is little chance of the
OL,8,FConservatives remaining in power and a
OL,9,Fstrong possibility of Labour forming
OL,10,Fthe next government.
OL,12,FThe idea of a Labour government
OL,13,Fabolishing the BBC as we know it or
OL,14,Fpushing it down a commercially funded
OL,15,Froute is for the birds.
OL,17,FFor all the rows it has had with the
OL,18,FBBC over the years, its support for
OL,19,Fthe principle of a publicly funded
OL,20,Fpublic service broadcaster has never
OL,21,Fbeen in doubt.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G9/12
