OL,3,CRadio 4 LW/MW, linear BBC services and
OL,4,Cfuture BBC funding
OL,6,FIn contrast, some on the right have
OL,7,Falways been highly sceptical or
OL,8,Fdownright hostile even though more
OL,9,Fpragmatic politicians have always
OL,10,Fmanaged to keep them in check.
OL,12,FAll mainstream political parties are
OL,13,Fbroad churches and care about
OL,14,Fundecided "swing" voters as well as
OL,15,Ftheir core supporters. They need to do
OL,16,Fthat to win and retain power.
OL,18,FAbolishing the BBC as we know it is
OL,19,Fnot a vote winner despite what some in
OL,20,Fecho chambers may imagine.
