OL,3,CRadio 4 LW/MW, linear BBC services and
OL,4,Cfuture BBC funding
OL,6,FAnd please do not confuse popular
OL,7,Fprogrammes or hits with the BBC
OL,8,Fbecoming more commercial.
OL,10,FThat is the easiest form of attack for
OL,11,Fopponents. Some would love nothing
OL,12,Fmore than to see the BBC reduced to
OL,13,Fniche, specialist and deadly serious
OL,14,Foutput for small audiences. Mainstream
OL,15,Fbroadcasting would be left to the
OL,16,Fmarket.
OL,18,FTo suggest popular hits should not be
OL,19,Fpart of the mix is to suggest a
OL,20,Ffundamentally different role for the
OL,21,FBBC.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G11/12
